{"title":"追星","authors":["向求纬"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":4,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"追星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向求纬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌和星连在一起的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篝火正在草地上燃烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支横笛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将二万五千里的光芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻悄悄缀在八角帽上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"影和星第一次相遇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是在一排窑洞门口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随便撑开一块银幕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊毛肚头巾　旱烟袋儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磕出一些火花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不小心溅上了那些军帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实那时就在追了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追浩歌中的红星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追光影中的红星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国革命　好紧迫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不跑步不行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不追赶不行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好容易追进　一辆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放牌汽车的驾驶室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有位战友　以三月五日为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低头擦拭方向盘的当儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶上　星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那车开到川滇边界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九十年代　匕首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十四次出没的瞬间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五角形的星　带血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"环宇骤然间通红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果全身心追赶雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜幕上怎能不繁星满天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果高速度追赶徐洪刚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荡涤邪恶便不在话下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实何须苦苦追寻啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心与心——近在咫尺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人偏偏吝啬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举手之劳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是都愿做流星么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就划出你的轨迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴之以歌　伴之以影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓦然回首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才发觉你我谁不是明星"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}